messageBody:
The following junit poll is now closed. Here are the
final results:


POLL QUESTION: JUNIT was introduced in your company.
What effect did it have on the project
duration ?

CHOICES AND RESULTS
- reduction of duration, 6 votes, 42.86%
- benefit after first attempt, 5 votes, 35.71%
- longer duration (with better quality), 1 votes, 7.14%
- no change in duration, 2 votes, 14.29%
